#: serverguide/C/security.xml:245(para)
msgid ""
"To set any of these values, simply use the following syntax, and follow the "
"interactive prompts:"
msgstr ""
"Para establecer alguno de esos valores, simplemente use la sintaxis "
"siguiente, y responda a las preguntas interactivas:"

#: serverguide/C/security.xml:249(command)
msgid "sudo chage username"
msgstr "sudo chage nombre de usuario"

#: serverguide/C/security.xml:251(para)
msgid ""
"The following is also an example of how you can manually change the explicit "
"expiration date (-E) to 01/31/2008, minimum password age (-m) of 5 days, "
"maximum password age (-M) of 90 days, inactivity period (-I) of 5 days after "
