"Para más información vea la <ulink url=\"http://www.openldap.org/\">Página "
"web de OpenLDAP</ulink>"

#: serverguide/C/network-auth.xml:1194(para)
msgid ""
"Though starting to show it's age, a great source for in depth LDAP "
